description:
The Mother's Choice Flair II Convertible Booster is designed to grow with your child.

Suitable from 6 months to 8 years of age approximately.

Features include easy one-handed lift for 5 position headrest adjustment and 6 point safety harness that can be removed and stowed out of the way when transitioning to booster mode. Also narrow seat design to accommodate 3 across the back seat in most cars. 2 years warranty on the cover & 6 year warranty on the hardware for your peace of mind.

Product Features:
  • Suitable from 6 months to approx 8 yrs of age
  • Simple belt path for easy installation
  • 2 large swing out cup holders
  • 6 point safety harness that can be removed and stowed out of the way when tranisitioning to booster mode
  • Narrow seat design to accommodate 3 across the back in most cars
  • Reclinable back for a better fitment into most cars
  • Removable and machine washable cover and infant insert for easy cleaning
name: Mother's Choice 1EA
